====================================================================================================
CHARACTER SKILLS GUIDE - ALL CHARACTERS
R Characters (18) | SR Characters (56) | SSR Characters (161) | Total: 235
====================================================================================================

====================================================================================================
STATUS EFFECTS & DEBUFFS REFERENCE
====================================================================================================

【CROWD CONTROL (Cannot Act)】
  • Petrify     - Unable to act, Block reduced to 0
  • Stun        - Unable to act
  • Freeze      - Unable to act + HP damage per second (-150 to -700/s depending on level)
  • Sleep       - Unable to act. Wakes when damaged, but that hit is a guaranteed CRIT

【CONTROL (Limited Actions)】
  • Silence     - Can only normal attack, cannot use Skills or Ultimate
  • Confusion   - Attacks random targets (allies or enemies), cannot use Ultimate
  • Charm       - Attacks allies instead of enemies, cannot use Ultimate
  • Taunt       - Forces enemy to attack the taunter

【DAMAGE OVER TIME】
  • Poison      - HP damage per second (-80 to -300/s depending on level)
  • Burn        - HP damage per second (-50 to -200/s depending on level), STACKABLE
  • Bleed       - HP damage per second (-1% HP + flat damage)

【STAT REDUCTION】
  • Paralysis   - Action Speed -50%, Physical ATK -50%, Magic ATK -50%
  • Curse       - Cannot recover HP/MP, Action Speed -50%, Critical Rate = 0
  • Blind       - Block = 0, Accuracy -50%
  • Fear        - MP drain per second (-20 to -100/s depending on level)

【OTHER】
  • Cleanse/Dispel - Removes all buffs from target

====================================================================================================
BUFF LEVEL VALUES REFERENCE
====================================================================================================

【Attack Buffs】 (format: +%/+flat)
  Lv1: +10%/+20 | Lv2: +12%/+25 | Lv3: +15%/+30 | Lv4: +18%/+35 | Lv5: +20%/+40

【Defense Buffs】 (format: +%/+flat)
  Lv1: +10%/+15 | Lv2: +12%/+20 | Lv3: +15%/+25 | Lv4: +18%/+30 | Lv5: +20%/+35

【Block Buffs】
  Lv1: +5 | Lv2: +7 | Lv3: +9 | Lv4: +11 | Lv5: +13 | LvMax: +15

【Action Speed Buffs】
  Lv1: +7 | Lv2: +11 | Lv3: +14 | Lv4: +17 | Lv5: +20

【Critical Damage Buffs】
  Physical: Lv1: +300 | Lv2: +400 | Lv3: +450 | Lv4: +500 | Lv5: +550
  Magic:    Lv1: +400 | Lv2: +500 | Lv3: +580 | Lv4: +640 | Lv5: +700

【Element Damage Taken+ (Debuff on Enemy)】
  Lv1: +10% | Lv2: +13% | Lv3: +16% | Lv4: +18% | Lv5: +20%
